Posted By: scott brockelman
I am thinking of selling my 1911 Obak set which is complete in nice mid grade condition. All raw except Weaver which is a PSA 5. I would consider selling with or without the Weaver. The set breaks down as follows:

P/F 3 cards
G 10 cards
VG 15 cards
Vg/Ex 32 cards
EX 60 cards
EXMT 39 cards 
NRMT 10 cards

Interested parties are asked to email for more information.

Scott
